- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is also likely as the scan matching SLAM problem involves processing sensor data to create a map of the environment. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is relevant as the IEKF is a control algorithm used to estimate the state of the robot. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is possible as the IEKF is a type of machine learning algorithm. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also possible as the IEKF is a type of AI algorithm used for state estimation.
